                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2004-05-05</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This little book cracks me up--love the retro look and read--but definitely not a serious 'how-to' for people seeking fashion advice. I have an original printing of it, and this reprint looks identicle--except the cover colors. Read it and you'll feel 1000% thrilled to be a chick of the '90s!</span>
                  
              
